__''Flux Capacity Node Farmers - WVW Log Review''__ The following stats are computed over 14 out of 14 fights. Squad overall killed 186 enemies and had 280 deaths, Illusioned 12 downs, did 59,365,236 damage, took 51,142,017 damage, ripped 9,697 boons, cleansed 24,393 conditions, generated 43m 20s of stability, generated 12m 50s of protection, generated 6m 26s of aegis, generated 4h 31m 27s of might, generated 12m 12s of fury, generated 4m 3s of resistance, generated 10m 49s of resolution, generated 8m 37s of quickness, generated 23m 29s of swiftness, generated 6m 24s of alacrity, generated 14m 33s of vigor, generated 20m 16s of regeneration, healed for 12,048,669, generated 892,380 barrier over a total time of 40m 5s in 14 fights. Kill Death Ratio for the session was ''0.66''. There were between 42 and 50 allied players involved (average 46.1 players).
